title: Aerial America S01E02
description:
Aerial America gives an unparalleled view of United states treasured landmarks and breathtaking landscapes. Aerial America is a television series airing on the Smithsonian Channel. Each episode is an aerial video tour of a U.S. state. It consists entirely of aerial scenes with no ground-level shots, and is narrated. Flyovers of natural areas such as national parks are included along with well-known buildings and urban areas.

The series is being shot using the Cineflex V14 gimbal-stabilized video camera system.
